name: Nangoli Jude Eric
about: Hello! my name is Nangoli Jude Eric, a father and a self-taught Front-End Developer/UI Designer based in Spencer, Building user-friendly applications is truly a passion of mine, I love writing clean and efficient maintainable code. When I’m not working, I’m either: Looking for the latest techniques, having some good time with my family, working out in the gym or talking to friends. I’m simple and social person, I love travelling, looking at beautiful arts and paintings.
